Event.info: OSINT Fidelis Threat Advisory #1018 Looking at the Sky for a DarkComet from the Fidelis Cybersecurity

Attribute.value:
rule DarkComet
{
meta:
description = "DarkComet RAT"
author = "Fidelis Cybersecurity"
date = "2015-07-22"
strings:
$s1 = "#KCMDDC"
$s2 = "DCDATA"
$s3 = "#BOT#CloseServer"
$s4 = "#BOT#SvrUninstall"
$s5 = "#BOT#URLDownload"
condition:
uint16(0) == 0x5a4d and filesize < 50MB and all of ($s*)
}
